<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 31 at 10:02AM EST  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...Locally Dense Fog...
Foggy conditions continue across portions of eastern New York and
western New England with some locally dense fog resulting in
visibilities of less than a half of a mile at times. Motorists are
urged to allow for extra time to get to their destination and
leave plenty of space between vehicles. Conditions will continue
gradually improve this morning.</description>
